metadata.name: Mapmaker's Archipelago
metadata.description:
Taste some of the best levels submitted by the community.
Beware that most of them are extremely challenging!

metadata.name: Dead Islands
metadata.description: The Heart of Darkness awaits the brave!

metadata.name: Unstable Vortex
metadata.description:
The fabric of reality is warped around the Unstable Vortex.
Weird and unusual islands sometimes emerge.
Most of them sink back into the depths before too long.
Explore them while you have the chance!

metadata.name: Tutorial
metadata.description:
Learn the basics of the game
while confronting the menace of
Godfrey the Goose.

metadata.name: Islands of Pain
metadata.description:
Rare souls lose themselves in the Islands of Pain.
Those looking for true challenge,
those that find joy in suffering...
Is this a place for you?

metadata.name: Old World
metadata.description:
The days of glory are long gone in the Old World.
The crumbling kingdoms are weak and ripe for conquest.
Do you have what it takes?

manifest.name: Invasion
manifest.description: One island overlooks the rest of its cluster. Once you claim it, the rest will fall in line.
manifest.author: @lovalmidas

manifest.name: Locked In
manifest.description: Recent bandit uprising left your kingdom shattered and stifled. Take back your land and show everybody why you were the king here.
manifest.author: @MykhailoBarabash

manifest.name: Before Bed Time
manifest.description: with special thanks to @alexvornoffice
manifest.author: @adamjarn

manifest.name: Knights before Christmas
manifest.description: Oh Christmas trees, oh Christmas trees, how golden are your branches! But could you gift me more cash please, I need to pay my armies?
manifest.author: @PositronicBranez

manifest.name: Theory of Colors
manifest.description: COLOOOOOOOOOOORRRRRRSSSSSSSSSSS
manifest.author: @ravageur

manifest.name: Norman Conquest
manifest.description: Defeat the two Harolds and unify England!
manifest.author: @Arran

manifest.name: Guerilla Warfare
manifest.description: Defeat the Lord and your fellow bandits.
manifest.author: @Arran

manifest.name: Hexed forest
manifest.description: Legends speak of abandoned gold mines hidden within the cursed woods. Navigating mystic thickets may be difficult, but your scouts found some safe passages. Unfortunately, they also found competitors.
manifest.author: @MykhailoBarabash

manifest.name: Last Hope
manifest.description: The Green, Brown, and Grey king were wiped out in a blink of an eye. They could not even slow down the advance of the red king. Our Army has been defeated too, and the beige King has not yet started to build an army. The Red King rules all mighty, no one has an Army that could oppose his. We are outmatched.
manifest.author: @HumblyMe

manifest.name: Farmers Army
manifest.description: Can nine pawns defeat four knights?
manifest.author: @HumblyMe

manifest.name: Arrival
manifest.description: Just another island to clear of zombies. Or is it?...

manifest.name: Hammer of Faith
manifest.description: We've caught up with Rosaline the Righteous, let's help her turn the tide!

manifest.name: Harvest
manifest.description: A large island littered with Haunted Towns. Rosaline is going to be busy...

manifest.name: City of the Dead
manifest.description: With undead emerging from the sewers, is there still time to save this City?

manifest.name: Heart of Darkness
manifest.description: The home base of the Necromantic Cult. It's do or die time!

manifest.name: Merry Christmas
manifest.description: ...and Happy New Year 2024!

manifest.name: Nomad
manifest.description: You can build new towns on this island!

manifest.name: Knight Fight
manifest.description: Units on this island are much cheaper to maintain!

manifest.name: Occupation
manifest.description: True conquerors capture towns, not raze them!

manifest.name: Brave Sir Robin
manifest.description: On this island you can bravely run away from battle even when not protected by walls.

manifest.name: Swamped
manifest.description: Introducing a new terrain type to Konkr! Swamp produces no income and cannot support castles or knights.

manifest.name: Gold Rush
manifest.description: Can you control the rich gold mines on this Island?

manifest.name: Easter Egg
manifest.description: Catch the bunny if you can!

manifest.name: Regicide
manifest.description: Let the kings themselves battle it out!
